          .text
            %h3.name GoTruckerGo
            %p GoTruckerGo is the easiest and most cost effective way for trucking companies, moving companies, hauling companies, or any company with a fleet, to manage and see all their Trucks, Trailers, Drivers, Brokers, Invoices, Repairs, Receipts, Shipments, and Payments in an “all-in-one” dashboard.
            %p And the best part is there is no pricey software to purchase and download, nothing to integrate, nothing to keep you tied to your desk because GoTruckerGo can be accessed anywhere from any computer, anytime day or night!
        .service
          .icon
            = image_tag '/assets/css/icons/icol32/trucks-trailers.png'
          .text
            %h3.name TRUCKS & TRAILERS
            %p Manage and track all the information you’ll ever need for each truck and trailer you’ll ever have. With GoTruckerGo you can store VIN numbers, inspection dates, engine/transmission type, axle capacity, suspension, size/width and gross vehicle weight ratios. Plus, upload and store important documents such as insurance certificates, inspection reports, registrations, and even truck photos for easy identification. You’ll never need to fidget through files looking for information on your trucks or trailers again!
        .service
