            = image_tag '/assets/css/icons/icol32/driver50.png'
          .text
            %h3.name DRIVERS
            %p Your drivers may come and go but your driver information will always be at your fingertips. With GoTruckerGo you’ll be able to track each driver along with their contacts, social security number, driver’s license, CDL’s, hire and release dates, pay rates and more. Plus upload their driver’s license and certificates, medical records, emergency contacts, and each driver’s mug-shot so you can always match the face to the name. 
        .service
