            = image_tag '/assets/css/icons/icol32/broker50.png'
          .text
            %h3.name BROKERS
            %p Managing and keeping track of your Brokers’ contact and information is now so simple. GoTruckerGo allows you to easily store and manage your entire Brokers’ contact information, motor carrier numbers, and even upload carrier packets for immediate access.  
      .eight.columns
