            %p In one click GoTruckerGo allows you to assign each shipment; A broker, truck or trailer, driver, pick up and delivery date, price, load number, status, and invoice date. In one glance you’ll be able to track miles, number of stops, seal number, pallet quantity and have uploaded documents like load confirmation and bill of landing. 
        .service
