            = image_tag '/assets/css/icons/icol32/invoices50.png'
          .text
            %h3.name INVOICES
            %p You don’t have to be an office manager to manage all your invoices. With GoTruckerGo you can track your invoices by invoice numbers, prices, pickup dates, paid status, and paid dates. See what’s been paid and what is owed in a snapshot.
        .service
