        .service
          .icon
            = image_tag '/assets/css/icons/icol32/repairs50.png'
          .text
            %h3.name REPAIRS
            %p Following and managing repairs has always been a mess until now. GoTruckerGo allows you to easily follow and track each repair and assign it to a specific truck or trailer. All your service and parts provider information is at your finger-tips as well as delivery dates, payments, invoices, and costs for labor, parts, and service. Always know which truck or trailer is waiting for what part or service. 
